Building S.C.A.M

See doc/readme-qt.rst for instructions on building S.C.A.M QT,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of S.C.A.M.

See doc/build-*.txt for instructions on building S.C.A.Md,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of S.C.A.M.
